'''生成对抗网络'''（{{lang-en|'''G'''enerative '''A'''dversarial '''N'''etwork}}，简称{{lang|en|GAN}}）是[[非监督式学习|非监督式学习]]的一种方法，通过让两个[[人工神经网络|神经網路]]相互[[博弈论|博弈]]的方式进行学习。该方法由[[伊恩·古德费洛|伊恩·古德费洛]]等人于2014年提出。<ref name="MyUser_Arxiv.org_April_7_2016c"/>
生成對抗網絡由一個生成網絡與一個判別網絡組成。生成網絡從潛在空間（latent space）中隨機取樣作為輸入，其輸出結果需要盡量模仿訓練集中的真實樣本。判別網絡的輸入則為真實樣本或生成網絡的輸出，其目的是將生成網絡的輸出從真實樣本中盡可能分辨出來。而生成網絡則要盡可能地欺騙判別網絡。兩個網絡相互對抗、不斷調整參數，最終目的是使判別網絡無法判斷生成網絡的輸出結果是否真實。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://xinwen.eastday.com/a/170113081516834.html |title=能根據文字生成圖片的 GAN，深度學習領域的又一新星 |access-date=2018-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180415124917/http://xinwen.eastday.com/a/170113081516834.html |archive-date=2018-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="MyUser_Arxiv.org_April_7_2016c">{{cite arXiv|class=stat.ML|first2=Jean|last2=Pouget-Abadie|title=Generative Adversarial Networks|eprint=1406.2661|last1=Goodfellow|first1=Ian J.|last3=Mirza|first3=Mehdi|last4=Xu|first4=Bing|last5=Warde-Farley|first5=David|last6=Ozair|first6=Sherjil|last7=Courville|first7=Aaron|last8=Bengio|first8=Yoshua|year=2014}}</ref><ref name="OpenAI_com">{{citation |url=http://openai.com/blog/generative-models/ |title=Generative Models |publisher=[[OpenAI|OpenAI]] |date= |authors=Andrej Karpathy, Pieter Abbeel, Greg Brockman, Peter Chen, Vicki Cheung, Rocky Duan, Ian Goodfellow, Durk Kingma, Jonathan Ho, Rein Houthooft, Tim Salimans, John Schulman, Ilya Sutskever, And Wojciech Zaremba |accessdate=April 7, 2016 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422120206/https://openai.com/blog/generative-models/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[image:GAN_deepfake_white_girl.jpg|thumb]]
生成對抗網絡常用於生成以假亂真的圖片。<ref name="ITT_GANs">{{cite arXiv|eprint=1606.03498|title=Improved Techniques for Training GANs|last1=Salimans|first1=Tim|last2=Goodfellow|first2=Ian|last3=Zaremba|first3=Wojciech|last4=Cheung|first4=Vicki|last5=Radford|first5=Alec|last6=Chen|first6=Xi|class=cs.LG|year=2016}}</ref>此外，該方法還被用於生成影片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/vondrick/tinyvideo/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320105122/http://web.mit.edu/vondrick/tinyvideo/ |archive-date=2017-03-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、三維物體模型<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://3dgan.csail.mit.edu/ |title=3D Generative Adversarial Network<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2019-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027080206/http://3dgan.csail.mit.edu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>等。

生成對抗網絡虽然最开始提出是為了[[無監督學習|無監督學習]]，但经證明對{{link-en|半監督學習|Semi-supervised_learning}}<ref name="ITT_GANs" />、[[完全監督學習|完全監督學習]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Image-to-Image Translation with Conditional Adversarial Nets|url=https://phillipi.github.io/pix2pix/|first1=Phillip|last2=Zhu|first2=Jun-Yan|date=2017|journal=Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition|last3=Zhou|first3=Tinghui|last4=Efros|first4=Alexei|last1=Isola|access-date=2019-06-18|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414225155/https://phillipi.github.io/pix2pix/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 、[[強化學習|強化學習]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Generative Adversarial Imitation Learning|url=http://papers.nips.cc/paper/6391-generative-adversarial-imitation-learning|first1=Jonathon|last2=Ermon|first2=Stefano|journal=Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems|last1=Ho|access-date=2019-06-18|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019222917/http://papers.nips.cc/paper/6391-generative-adversarial-imitation-learning|dead-url=no}}</ref>也有效。 在2016年的一個研討會上，[[杨立昆|杨立昆]]称生成式對抗網絡为「機器學習這二十年來最酷的想法」。<ref>{{cite web|title=RL Seminar: The Next Frontier in AI: Unsupervised Learning|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbjF5VjniVE|last1=LeCun|first1=Yann|access-date=2019-06-18|archive-date=2020-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430143323/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbjF5VjniVE|dead-url=no}}</ref>

